    <text>
        <body>
            <div type="edition">
                <div type="textpart">
                    <ab>In nomine domini Dei eterni. <persName key="#Emperor/king" ref="#people/79"
                            >Hugo</persName> et <persName key="#Emperor/king" ref="#people/72"
                            >Lotharius</persName> gracia Dei <rs key="#Emperor/king">reges</rs>. Si
                        sacris ac venerabilibus locis ex nostrarum rerum facultatibus aliquid
                        conferimus, et collata a ceteris fidelibus confirmamus, presentis et eterne
                        vite gaudia adipisci non titubamus. Quapropter omnium sancte Dei Ecclesie
                        fidelium nostrorumque presencium ac futurorum comperiat solercia, <persName
                            key="#Intercessory #Bishops #fidelisOf"><name ref="Bruningus"
                                >Bruningum</name></persName>
                        <orgName ref="#juridical_persons/206"
                            key="#Rivers #Mountains #Casae/cassinae_massaricie #Landed_possessions #Forests #Fisheries #Mills #Wine #Hay/fodder #Castle #Walls #Defensive_elements #Churches #Royal_slave"
                            >sancte <placeName ref="#places/254">Astensis</placeName>
                            ecclesie</orgName> venerabilem <rs key="#Bishops">episcopum</rs>
                        dilectumque <rs key="#fidelisOf">fidelem</rs> nostrum nostram <rs
                            key="#Intercessory">exorasse</rs> clemenciam, quatinus prefate sancte
                        ecclesie in honore sancte Marie constructe quoddam <rs key="#Castle"
                            >castrum</rs> supra <placeName ref="#places/254">Astensem
                            civitatem</placeName> situm, quod <rs key="#Castle">Castellum Vetus</rs>
                        nuncupatur, cum <rs key="#Churches">capella</rs> in honore <orgName
                            key="#Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Object #Outflow #Iure_proprietatis/pleno_iure #Allocation_to_churches #Churches"
                            >sancti Ambrosii</orgName> ibidem edificata cum omnibus eius
                        pertinentiis, <rs key="#Landed_possessions">braydam</rs> quoque unam et <rs
                            key="#Hay/fodder">pratum</rs> unum iuxta <rs key="#Rivers">fluvium
                            Versa</rs>, ubi nuncupatur <placeName>Madingo</placeName>, et <rs
                            key="#Casae/cassinae_massaricie">massaricia</rs> sex cum <rs
                            key="#Royal_slave">servis et ancillis</rs> ea renitentibus per nostri
                        precepti paginam donare et concedere, cinfirmare quoque et corroborare
                        dignaremur. Cuius petitionibus libenter faventes, pro Dei amore animarumque
                        nostrarum remedio pretaxate sancte Astensi ecclesie per hoc nostrum
                        preceptum donamus, iuste et legaliter concedimus atque largimur, insuper
                        confirmamus et corroboramus predictum castrum, quod Castellum Vetus
                        nuncupatur, supra Astensem civitatem situm, cum predicta capella in honore
                        sancti Ambrosii edificata et omnibus rebus ibidem pertinentibus, cum <rs
                            key="#Walls">muris</rs> et <rs key="#Defensive_elements">fossatis</rs>,
                        cum brayda et prato, una cum casis et massariciis ac familiis utriusque
                        sexus, quorum nomina sunt: <persName key="#Royal_slave"><name ref="Secundus"
                                >Secundus</name></persName> cum muliere sua <persName
                            key="#Royal_slave"><name ref="Lovemperga">Lovemperga</name></persName>,
                            <persName key="#Royal_slave"><name ref="Resto">Resto</name></persName>
                        cum muliere sua <persName key="#Royal_slave"><name ref="Almalberga"
                                >Almelberga</name></persName>, <persName key="#Royal_slave"><name
                                ref="Astisianus">Astisianus</name></persName>, <persName
                            key="#Royal_slave"><name ref="Eugenia">Augenia</name></persName>,
                            <persName key="#Royal_slave"><name ref="Lubedeo"
                            >Lubedeo</name></persName>, <persName key="#Royal_slave"><name
                                ref="Hodo">Hodo</name></persName>, <persName key="#Royal_slave"
                                ><name ref="Georgius">Georgius</name></persName>, <persName
                            key="#Royal_slave"><name ref="Benedicta">Benedicta</name></persName>,
                            <persName key="#Royal_slave"><name ref="Iussimundus"
                            >Iussimundus</name></persName>, <persName key="#Royal_slave"><name
                                ref="Maziverga">Maziverga</name></persName>, <persName
                            key="#Royal_slave"><name ref="Grimaldus">Grimaldus</name></persName>,
                            <persName key="#Royal_slave"><name ref="Ingelberga"
                            >Ingelberga</name></persName>, cum filiis et filiabus illorum, seu cum
                        sediminibus, <rs key="#Landed_possessions">campis</rs>, <rs key="#Wine"
                            >vineis</rs>, terris, <rs key="#Hay/fodder">pratis</rs>, pascuis, <rs
                            key="#Forests">silvis</rs>, <rs key="#Rivers">aquis aquarumque
                            decursibus</rs>, <rs key="#Mills">molendinis</rs>, <rs key="#Fisheries"
                            >piscationibus</rs>, <rs key="#Mountains">montibus</rs>, vallibus,
                        planiciebus omnibusque rebus et familiis, totum in integrum, sicut superius
                        comprehensum est, funditus concedimus et omnino confirmamus. Si quis igitur
                        huius precepti violator extiterit, sciat se compositurum <rs key="#Penalty"
                            >auri optimi libras centum</rs>, <rs key="#Camera_regis">medietatem
                            camere nostre</rs> et <rs key="#Camera_of_other_public_authorities"
                            >medietatem parti predicte sancte Astensis ecclesie</rs>. Quod ut veius
                        credatur et diligencius observetur, manibus propriis roborantes anuli nostri
                        impressione subter insigniri fecimus. Signa serenissorum (M) (M) Hugonis et
                        Lotharii regum. <persName key="#Chancellor"><name ref="Giseprandus"
                                >Giseprandus</name></persName>
                        <rs key="#Chancellor">cancellarius</rs> ad vicem <persName
                            key="#Archchancellor #Bishops" ref="#people/1530">Azzonis</persName>
                        <rs key="#Bishops">episcopi</rs> et <rs key="#Archchancellor"
                            >archicancellarii</rs> recognovi et subscripsi. Data decimo kal.
                        augusti, anno incarnationis dominice DCCCCXXXVIII, anno domni Hugonis
                        piissimi regis XIII, Lotharii vero VIII, indicione XI. Actum <placeName
                            ref="#places/65">Papie</placeName>. Feliciter, amen.</ab>
                </div>
